      "heading": null,
      "description": "Grate your cheddar and also set aside."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Cook your instant noodles according to packet instructions. Drain using a sieve, saving the noodle-cooking water. Rinse the noodles with cold water."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pour a glug of vegetable oil into a pan and add in the kimchi, minced garlic and spring onions. Give it a good stir."
    },
